&lt;li&gt;Serve as a key liaison between partners and internal teams on developing joint go-to-market strategies and value propositions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist sales management in measuring and tracking effectiveness and consistency of partner focused efforts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner directly with regional sales representatives to develop and execute strategic partner engagement and growth initiatives within their territories.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assess inbound activity from new potential partners, working with leadership to qualify and diligence for inclusion in HYPR partner program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
