&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Senior DevOps Cloud Engineer to join our platform team and focus on automation.&amp;nbsp; We have an internally developed management tool written in Kotlin that needs to be extended to support advanced workflows.&amp;nbsp; You’ll be involved in the full life cycle support of our public cloud SaaS architecture.&amp;nbsp; You’ll have the opportunity to design, plan, build, extend, and support all new and existing cloud infrastructure.&amp;nbsp; The company’s platform is based on Kubernetes and your experience will be vital to the success of our customers.&amp;nbsp; Some examples of the internal services we support are code and artifact repositories, CI/CD runners, data warehouse, and tiered development environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As we grow we are adding new services and replacing or revamping old ones, and as such you’ll get to influence the way we adopt the design pillars of the organization: well-architected, secure, operationally efficient, and performant.&amp;nbsp; We believe AI has, and will continue to change the software industry, and we are weaving into our SDLC.&lt;/p&gt;
